room_title: Escape room "Adaleigh's Room" by Red Door Puzzle Rooms in Bowling Green
room_description: Want to play a game with Adaleigh? You were babysitting her when she locked you in her bedroom! She has left you clues to escape, but you only have an hour before Adaleigh trashes the house and her parents come back to see their daughter unattended. Can you escape in time to save your job?
